Firefox latest installation for centos 7

1.download latest version of  firefox-*.tar.bz2 

2.Remove the current firefox

yum remove firefox

unlink /usr/bin/firefox

mv /usr/bin/firefox /usr/bin/firefox_bak

3.cd /usr/local

tar xvjf firefox-56.0.1.tar.bz2

4.ln -s /usr/local/firefox/firefox /usr/bin/firefox
